  <summary>3/8/2001--Introduced.
Low Income Energy Reinvestment Act - Amends the Mineral Leasing Act to earmark for implementation of the Low-Income Home Energy Assistance Act of 1981 five percent of monies generated from sales, bonuses, royalties, and rentals of public lands (onshore Federal oil and natural gas revenues).</summary>
